{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setDragState:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@E@MLNAnnotationViewDragState","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationViewDragState","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"MLNAnnotationViewDragState"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"dragState"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"animated:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"animated"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can override this method to animate a custom annotation view as the user"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"drags it. As the system detects user actions that would indicate a drag, it"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"calls this method to update the drag state."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L279","fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h"},"title":"setDragState:animated:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setDragState:animated:","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(im)setDragState:animated:","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setDragState:animated:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationVie